<figureCitation id="F0842A44517772591896FC00D0ECFBC2" box="[159,224,1015,1040]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1354,1376]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,195,1329]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[151,1436,195,1329]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. A flower of Impatiens sp. (Balsaminaceae) being visited by unknown drosophilid flies. Adults of Lordiphosa anthophilia sp. nov. were collected from flowers of the same species." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1439523/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="57">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
